# Environment Variables for Vercel + Render Deployment

## Frontend Environment Variables (Vercel)
# Add these in Vercel Dashboard > Settings > Environment Variables

VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://mybudgeteer-backend.onrender.com/api

## Backend Environment Variables (Render)
# Add these in Render Dashboard > Environment

NODE_ENV=production
PORT=10000
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/mybudgeteer?retryWrites=true&w=majority
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secure-jwt-secret-at-least-32-characters-long
CLIENT_URL=https://mybudgeteer.vercel.app

# Optional: Additional Security
SESSION_SECRET=another-secure-secret-for-sessions
BCRYPT_ROUNDS=12
